text: Roza Guliyeva (born 28 March 1998) is an Azerbaijani footballer who plays as a midfielder for Georgian Women's Championship club FC Nike Tbilisi and the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriates in Georgia (country) Category:Expatriate footballers in Georgia (country)
